WEBVTT

00:01.235 --> 00:03.337
<i>PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i>ON "WAYWARD PINES"...</i>

00:03.337 --> 00:05.305
CLASS ONE OF THE ACADEMY.

00:05.305 --> 00:07.007
WELL, CONGRATULATIONS.
IT'S A REAL HONOR.
IT'S A RESPONSIBILITY.

00:07.007 --> 00:09.676
AND IF YOU BREAK THE RULES,
YOU HAVE TO BE RECKONED.

00:09.676 --> 00:12.446
Dr. Jenkins: WITHOUT
KATE BALLINGER, THEY'RE NOTHING.

00:12.446 --> 00:14.114
RECKON HER,
AND YOU COULD STOP ALL THIS.

00:14.114 --> 00:16.149
LOOK -- I TOLD YOU
I NEED TO DO THINGS MY WAY.

00:16.149 --> 00:18.385
YOU REMEMBER -- AS THE FIRST
GENERATION OF THIS TOWN,

00:18.385 --> 00:19.520
YOU ARE A LEADER NOW.

00:19.520 --> 00:21.021
Ben: THEY BROKE THE RULES

00:21.021 --> 00:22.256
AND THOSE RULES EXIST
FOR A REASON --

00:22.256 --> 00:24.224
WELL, WHEN IS YOUR DAD
GONNA RECKON THEM?

00:24.224 --> 00:25.626
HE'S NOT GOING TO.

00:25.626 --> 00:27.427
[ GRUNTS ]

00:27.427 --> 00:29.296
WE ARE JUST HERE
TO PROTECT WAYWARD PINES.

00:29.296 --> 00:30.564
GET OUT!

00:30.564 --> 00:31.565
UNH!
OH, GOD!

00:31.565 --> 00:34.201
AAH!
OHH!

00:34.201 --> 00:36.270
"ENJOY YOUR LIFE
IN WAYWARD PINES."

00:36.270 --> 00:38.105
I LOVE YOU.

00:38.672 --> 00:40.073
[ HIGH-PITCHED WHISTLING ]

00:40.073 --> 00:41.542
IF YOU REALLY
WANT TO PROTECT THEM,

00:41.542 --> 00:43.377
YOU HAVE TO STOP
PROTECTING ME.

00:43.377 --> 00:44.578
I CAN'T DO THAT.

00:44.578 --> 00:46.346
YOU HAVE TO PUT
AN END TO THIS.

00:46.346 --> 00:47.981
THERE'S SOMETHING
I HAVE TO SHOW YOU.

00:49.283 --> 00:51.652
<i>IT'S SEPTEMBER 15, 14:20.</i>

00:51.652 --> 00:53.086
AND ADAM
WAS JUST LEADING ONE GROUP.

00:53.086 --> 00:54.087
THERE ARE HUNDREDS.

00:54.087 --> 00:55.289
BELIEVE ME NOW?

00:56.757 --> 00:58.425
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:58.425 --> 00:59.993
I'M NOT GONNA KILL KATE.

00:59.993 --> 01:01.628
<i>AND THERE'S ONE MAN</i>
<i>BEHIND IT ALL.</i>

01:01.628 --> 01:04.131
<i>YOU KNOW HIM AS DR. JENKINS.</i>

01:04.131 --> 01:06.600
BUT HIS REAL NAME
IS DAVID PILCHER.

01:06.600 --> 01:08.502
[ CROWD GASPING,
KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

01:08.502 --> 01:09.703
WHAT HAPPENED TO THE POWER?

01:09.703 --> 01:11.738
[ KEY CLACKS ]

01:11.738 --> 01:13.040
[ SCREECHING ]

01:14.508 --> 01:16.610
[ LEAVES RUSTLING ]

01:28.589 --> 01:31.592
[ RUMBLING ]

02:35.288 --> 02:37.724
[ CROWD MURMURING ]
PAUL, YOU HAVE TO CALM DOWN.
IT'S OKAY.

02:37.724 --> 02:39.459
WE'RE GONNA GET THE POWER
BACK ON.

02:39.459 --> 02:41.595
WE'RE JUST TRYING TO FIGURE IT
OUT RIGHT NOW, ALL RIGHT?

02:41.595 --> 02:43.196
ALL RIGHT,
JUST -- JUST STAY CALM.

02:43.196 --> 02:44.665
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON UP THERE?

02:44.665 --> 02:46.199
What happened
to the lights?

02:46.199 --> 02:48.168
ETHAN, IT'S PAM.

02:48.168 --> 02:50.570
David shut down
the power grid.

02:50.570 --> 02:53.373
IS THE POWER OUT
AT THE FENCE, TOO?

02:53.373 --> 02:55.175
Yes.
Ethan, listen.

02:55.175 --> 02:57.144
YOU'VE GOT TO GET THOSE PEOPLE
OFF OF MAIN.

02:57.144 --> 02:59.312
WE'VE TRACKED SIX ABBIES
INSIDE THE PERIMETER,

02:59.312 --> 03:01.181
GOD KNOWS HOW MANY MORE
BEHIND THEM.

03:01.181 --> 03:02.516
WELL,
HOW MUCH TIME DO WE HAVE?

03:02.516 --> 03:04.117
JUST GET THEM
OUT OF THERE.

03:04.117 --> 03:05.385
COPY.

03:05.385 --> 03:08.388
[ MURMURING CONTINUES ]

03:09.990 --> 03:11.358
[ GASPS ]

03:11.358 --> 03:12.592
I'M GOING TO THE HOSPITAL
AND GETTING BEN.

03:12.592 --> 03:14.528
ALL RIGHT. GOOD.
MEET ME AT THE BUNKER.

03:14.528 --> 03:17.030
ALL RIGHT.

03:17.030 --> 03:18.432
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,
LISTEN UP!

03:18.432 --> 03:19.766
LISTEN!

03:19.766 --> 03:21.735
WE CAN'T STAY HERE.
IT'S NOT SAFE, OKAY?

03:21.735 --> 03:25.005
WE GOT TO START MOVING EAST.

03:25.005 --> 03:28.408
THERE'S AN UNDERGROUND BUNKER AT
THE CORNER OF BOXWOOD AND THIRD

03:28.408 --> 03:30.243
IN A VACANT LOT
UNDER A SHED.

03:30.243 --> 03:31.545
THAT'S WHERE WE'LL MEET.

03:31.545 --> 03:34.014
LET'S GO.

03:34.014 --> 03:35.115
BOXWOOD AND THIRD!
LET'S GO!

03:35.115 --> 03:36.283
ALL RIGHT.

03:36.283 --> 03:38.552
HEY, HEY, HEY,
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:38.552 --> 03:40.420
PILCHER.
HE PULLED THE PLUG.

03:40.420 --> 03:42.556
THE POWER'S DOWN
AT THE FENCE.

03:42.556 --> 03:44.191
LET'S GO.
WE GOT TO MOVE.

03:44.191 --> 03:45.492
OKAY,
WE NEED WEAPONS.

03:45.492 --> 03:46.693
WHERE'S YOUR GROUP?

03:46.693 --> 03:48.562
TIM?
OKAY, YOU GET EVERYBODY ELSE.

03:48.562 --> 03:51.098
YOU MEET US AT THE
SHERIFF'S STATION, ALL RIGHT?

03:51.098 --> 03:53.467
[ COMPUTERS BEEPING ]

03:53.467 --> 03:57.237
SHOW ME
OUTSIDE THE PERIMETER.

03:57.237 --> 03:59.239
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

04:07.247 --> 04:09.249
HOW MUCH LONGER
TILL POWER'S RESTORED?

04:09.249 --> 04:10.617
20 MINUTES,
MAYBE LONGER.

04:10.617 --> 04:13.153
I DON'T KNOW
IF WE HAVE THAT LONG.

04:14.221 --> 04:15.989
[ ELECTRICITY HUMS ]

04:15.989 --> 04:18.625
WH-WHAT'S GOING ON?

04:18.625 --> 04:20.060
AMY.

04:20.060 --> 04:21.762
STOP, STOP. DON'T --
D-DON'T TRY AND MOVE.

04:21.762 --> 04:22.763
DON'T TRY AND MOVE.

04:22.763 --> 04:24.297
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

04:24.297 --> 04:26.066
WHAT HAPPENED?
UH...

04:26.066 --> 04:28.635
YOU HAD TO
GO INTO SURGERY.

04:28.635 --> 04:32.072
TH-THEY FOUND SOME BLEEDING
OR -- OR SOMETHING,

04:32.072 --> 04:34.040
I DON'T --
I DON'T KNOW.

04:36.676 --> 04:38.678
IT'S OKAY, THOUGH.
YOU'RE OKAY.

04:38.678 --> 04:39.679
OKAY.

04:39.679 --> 04:41.748
I WAS SO SCARED.

04:41.748 --> 04:45.385
I...I DIDN'T WANT
TO LOSE YOU.

04:47.521 --> 04:50.323
YEAH,
ME EITHER.

04:50.323 --> 04:51.758
YOU'RE OKAY,
THOUGH.

04:51.758 --> 04:53.560
[ SIGHS ]

04:53.560 --> 04:55.295
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]
Theresa: BEN?

04:55.295 --> 04:57.497
YOU GUYS,
WE HAVE TO GET OUT OF HERE.

04:57.497 --> 04:59.332
WHAT'S GOING ON?
CAN SHE MOVE?

04:59.332 --> 05:00.734
I -- I DON'T --
I DON'T THINK SO.

05:00.734 --> 05:02.335
I'M NOT LEAVING HER.

05:02.335 --> 05:03.670
I HAVE TO STAY WITH HER,
MOM.

05:03.670 --> 05:05.205
I KNOW,
SWEETHEART.

05:05.205 --> 05:06.339
WE'RE NOT GONNA
LEAVE HER BEHIND, OKAY?

05:06.339 --> 05:07.440
WHERE'S DR. CAROL?

05:13.747 --> 05:15.582
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

05:15.582 --> 05:18.151
[ COUGHING ]

05:24.191 --> 05:27.194
[ GROANS ]

05:30.397 --> 05:33.166
[ KEYS JINGLING ]

05:37.103 --> 05:40.173
HEY,
WHAT'S GOING ON OUT THERE?

05:40.173 --> 05:42.576
IS THE POWER OUT
AT THE FENCE?

05:53.520 --> 05:54.654
OH,
I'VE GOT THIS, TOO.

05:54.654 --> 05:57.224
UM...FRANKLIN
WASN'T FINISHED YET,

05:57.224 --> 05:58.658
BUT I'M PRETTY CERTAIN
THAT IT'LL DETONATE.

05:58.658 --> 06:01.628
YOU JUST,
UH, ARM THESE.

06:07.434 --> 06:09.669
THIS MIGHT
COME IN HANDY.

06:09.669 --> 06:12.005
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

06:12.005 --> 06:13.740
Man: OKAY, NO PROBLEM.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

06:13.740 --> 06:15.709
THANK YOU BOTH.

06:15.709 --> 06:17.010
DAVID.

06:17.010 --> 06:18.078
PAM.
WHA--

06:18.078 --> 06:20.146
MY DEAR, DEAR PAM.
WHA--

06:20.146 --> 06:22.415
THANK GOODNESS
YOU'RE HERE.

06:22.415 --> 06:24.150
WE NEED
TO DISCUSS PREPARATIONS

06:24.150 --> 06:25.652
FOR THE AWAKENING
OF GROUP "C."

06:25.652 --> 06:26.753
GROUP "C"?

06:26.753 --> 06:29.089
THOSE ARE OUR PEOPLE
OUT THERE.

06:29.089 --> 06:30.724
THEY'RE GONNA BE KILLED,
EVERY LAST ONE OF THEM.

06:30.724 --> 06:32.292
YOU'VE GOT TO
TURN THE POWER BACK ON.

06:32.292 --> 06:33.526
YOU'VE GOT TO END THIS.
I CAN'T.

06:33.526 --> 06:35.428
IT'S TOO LATE.

06:35.428 --> 06:38.565
I-I-I WISH I COULD,
BUT I CAN'T.

06:38.565 --> 06:42.702
THIS TOWN WE'VE CREATED, PAM,
IT'S TOO SICK.

06:42.702 --> 06:45.038
THEY'RE ALREADY DYING.

06:45.038 --> 06:49.075
I FAILED THEM.
I-I FAILED US.

06:49.075 --> 06:52.145
THEY'RE LOST,
JUST AS GROUP "A" WAS LOST,

06:52.145 --> 06:55.015
BUT --
BUT WE <i>CAN</i> BEGIN AGAIN.

06:55.015 --> 06:59.019
IN THE WINTER, ONCE
THE ABERRATIONS HAVE MIGRATED,

06:59.019 --> 07:01.221
THEN WE COULD START AGAIN
FROM A CLEAN SLATE.

07:01.221 --> 07:03.690
NO MORE OF THIS --
THIS DECADENCE.

07:03.690 --> 07:06.459
NO MORE SHERIFF POPE
OR ETHAN BURKE.

07:06.459 --> 07:07.560
YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT HIM.

07:07.560 --> 07:09.062
I WAS WRONG.
I MADE A MISTAKE.

07:09.062 --> 07:11.564
AND THERE WILL ALWAYS
BE MISTAKES, DAVID.

07:11.564 --> 07:14.034
BUT THERE IS STILL TIME
TO FIX THIS.

07:14.034 --> 07:16.369
PERHAPS.
YES.

07:16.369 --> 07:20.974
IF WE LEARN,
WE CAN START AGAIN.

07:20.974 --> 07:23.743
WE NEED TO TAKE
MORE DIRECT RESPONSIBILITY,

07:23.743 --> 07:26.112
YOU AND I.

07:26.112 --> 07:27.547
LIKE THE EARLY DAYS.

07:27.547 --> 07:30.483
WE'RE NOT TALKING
ABOUT IDEAS HERE ANYMORE, DAVID.

07:30.483 --> 07:34.354
WE ARE TALKING ABOUT
ACTUAL, LIVING HUMAN BEINGS!

07:34.354 --> 07:37.757
I FOLLOWED YOU FOR YEARS,
DOWN EVERY ROAD, BLINDLY,

07:37.757 --> 07:40.694
BUT THIS IS TOO FAR.

07:40.694 --> 07:43.463
YOU HAVE NOT FAILED.

07:43.463 --> 07:46.733
YOUR GREAT EXPERIMENT
IS WORKING.

07:46.733 --> 07:50.203
ALL YOU'VE GOT TO DO NOW
IS JUST...

07:50.203 --> 07:53.006
LET IT GO.

07:54.441 --> 07:57.477
TURN THE POWER BACK ON,
DAVID.

07:57.477 --> 08:00.480
YOU SEND THE GUARDS DOWN
TO HELP THOSE PEOPLE.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.716
JUST END THIS.

08:05.185 --> 08:07.053
YES.

08:07.053 --> 08:08.555
YEAH.

08:08.555 --> 08:10.457
THE GUARDS.

08:10.457 --> 08:12.692
THE GUARDS.

08:12.692 --> 08:13.994
WE NEED THE GUARDS
IN HERE.

08:13.994 --> 08:15.095
IN HERE?

08:15.095 --> 08:17.030
WHAT -- WE DON'T NEED YOU
IN HERE.

08:17.030 --> 08:18.331
WE NEED YOU TO GO DOWN
TO INTO THE --
TAKE HER TO SUSPENSION.

08:18.331 --> 08:19.432
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

08:19.432 --> 08:20.433
COME ON.

08:20.433 --> 08:22.435
DAVID!

08:22.435 --> 08:25.372
UNH! DAVID!
WHAT?! DAVID!

08:27.307 --> 08:28.441
[ GUN COCKS ]

08:28.441 --> 08:31.044
Guard: EVERYBODY,
HANDS IN THE AIR!

08:31.044 --> 08:32.545
HANDS UP!

08:32.545 --> 08:34.247
UP, UP, UP!
EVERYBODY!

08:34.247 --> 08:37.384
HANDS IN THE AIR!

08:37.384 --> 08:40.387
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

08:47.160 --> 08:49.162
SHE'S DOING WELL FOR A GIRL
WHO JUST HAD MAJOR SURGERY,

08:49.162 --> 08:50.630
BUT WE SHOULDN'T BE
MOVING HER ANYWHERE.

08:50.630 --> 08:52.098
SHE'S TOO WEAK.

08:52.098 --> 08:53.566
OH, DOCTOR,
WE DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

08:53.566 --> 08:55.001
BEN,
CAN YOU GRAB MY STUFF?

08:55.001 --> 08:57.070
OKAY, SO, WHAT CAN WE DO
TO KEEP HER STABLE?

08:58.371 --> 09:00.540
[ ELECTRICITY HUMS ]

09:03.376 --> 09:05.478
IT'S THE GENERATOR.
UM, I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

09:12.652 --> 09:14.988
[ SIGHS ]

09:17.023 --> 09:19.426
I'LL MEET YOU
AT THE BUNKER.

09:19.426 --> 09:20.527
BE CAREFUL.

09:20.527 --> 09:23.463
YOU TOO.

09:24.664 --> 09:26.232
ALL RIGHT,
GUYS.

09:26.232 --> 09:28.234
LET'S GET AS MANY PEOPLE
OFF THE STREET AS WE CAN.

09:28.234 --> 09:31.404
Jason: PILCHER ALWAYS SAID
THIS DAY WOULD COME.

09:32.605 --> 09:37.644
HE WARNED US THAT ONE DAY, THERE
WOULD BE A DAY OF RECKONING.

09:37.644 --> 09:42.115
AND ON THAT DAY, HE WOULD SAVE
THE FIRST GENERATION.

09:42.115 --> 09:43.983
BUT EVERYONE ELSE...

09:43.983 --> 09:46.586
THE WEAK...

09:46.586 --> 09:49.522
WOULD DROWN.

09:49.522 --> 09:52.992
JUST LIKE YOU.

09:52.992 --> 09:56.096
JUST LIKE YOUR HUSBAND.

09:58.131 --> 10:00.400
[ GUN COCKS ]

10:02.969 --> 10:06.272
WE'RE DONE HERE.

10:07.640 --> 10:11.077
HEY,
YOU CAN'T JUST LEAVE US IN HERE!

10:11.077 --> 10:12.212
LET US OUT!

10:12.212 --> 10:14.280
LET US OUT!

10:29.362 --> 10:30.497
[ GENERATOR BUZZING ]

10:30.497 --> 10:32.465
[ KEY CLICKING ]

10:33.500 --> 10:34.467
[ SCREAMS ]

10:40.206 --> 10:43.209
[ "L'ELISIR D'AMORE:
UNA FURTIVA LAGRIMA" PLAYS ]

10:45.311 --> 10:52.485
♪ <i>UNA FURTIVA LAGRIMA</i> ♪

10:55.321 --> 10:59.159
♪ <i>NEGLI OCCHI SUOI SPUNTO</i> ♪

10:59.159 --> 11:01.060
[ GLASS CLINKING ]

11:01.060 --> 11:03.730
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

11:03.730 --> 11:09.002
♪ <i>QUELLE FESTOSE</i> ♪

11:09.002 --> 11:11.037
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

11:11.037 --> 11:12.672
[ SCREAMING CONTINUES ]

11:15.441 --> 11:18.611
[ GRUNTS ]

11:20.313 --> 11:21.581
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

11:21.581 --> 11:24.150
♪ <i>CHE PIU CERCANDO IO VO?</i> ♪

11:24.150 --> 11:26.419
[ ABBY ROARS ]

11:26.419 --> 11:28.254
[ GRUNTS ]

11:28.254 --> 11:32.025
♪ <i>CHE PIU CERCANDO IO VO?</i> ♪

11:40.700 --> 11:42.202
[ LOUD CLATTER ]

11:42.202 --> 11:43.269
[ GASPS ]

11:44.470 --> 11:46.239
OKAY.

11:46.239 --> 11:48.074
WE HAVE TO GO NOW.
WE HAVE TO HURRY.

11:48.074 --> 11:50.009
WE HAVE TO HURRY.
OKAY? OKAY, YOU GUYS?

11:50.009 --> 11:51.244
COME ON. LET'S GO.

11:53.646 --> 11:55.548
[ GASPING ]

11:59.419 --> 12:01.554
GO ON!

12:01.554 --> 12:02.655
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

12:02.655 --> 12:06.226
[ ABBY GROWLS ]

12:08.127 --> 12:11.297
[ GLASS SHATTERING ]

12:13.366 --> 12:16.369
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

12:16.369 --> 12:18.304
[ ABBY GROWLS ]

12:20.506 --> 12:22.108
[ SCREAMING ]

12:22.108 --> 12:24.077
[ ABBY GROWLS ]

12:24.077 --> 12:26.579
[ ABBY SCREAMS ]

12:26.579 --> 12:28.081
OH! OH!

12:28.081 --> 12:29.215
RUN! GO! NOW!

12:29.215 --> 12:31.217
GET TO THE BUNKER!
GO!

12:31.217 --> 12:33.052
[ ABBIES SCREAM ]

12:33.052 --> 12:36.489
HOW HAS HE CONVINCED YOU
TO DO THIS?

12:38.992 --> 12:41.127
CHRISTINA.

12:41.127 --> 12:43.129
I KNOW YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING YOUR DUTY.

12:43.129 --> 12:44.330
BUT YOU'RE NOT.

12:44.330 --> 12:46.266
THINGS HAVE GONE
TERRIBLY WRONG.

12:46.266 --> 12:47.467
WE JUST --

12:47.467 --> 12:49.002
DO WHAT SHE SAYS
AND SHUT YOUR MOUTH.

12:49.002 --> 12:52.005
ROBERT,
THIS GOES FOR YOU, TOO.

12:52.005 --> 12:53.673
IT GOES
FOR ALL OF US.

12:53.673 --> 12:55.074
PAUL.

12:55.074 --> 12:58.378
WE ALL GAVE UP OUR LIVES
IN THE OLD WORLD

12:58.378 --> 13:02.148
TO JOIN DAVID PILCHER
ON THIS JOURNEY OF HIS.

13:02.148 --> 13:03.583
AND IT'S WORKING.

13:03.583 --> 13:05.752
IN TOWN THIS YEAR,
THERE WERE MORE PREGNANCIES

13:05.752 --> 13:08.321
THAN EVER BEFORE
IN WAYWARD PINES.

13:08.321 --> 13:12.191
THE FUTURE,
OUR FIRST GENERATION,

13:12.191 --> 13:16.663
THAT IS THE FUTURE FOR ALL
OF US, OUR DUTY TO <i>MANKIND.</i>

13:16.663 --> 13:18.598
NOT TO DAVID PILCHER.

13:18.598 --> 13:20.099
DAVID IS OUR SAVIOR.

13:20.099 --> 13:22.602
DAVID IS NOT
A SAVIOR.

13:22.602 --> 13:24.337
HE'S NOT A GOD.

13:24.337 --> 13:26.572
HE'S JUST A MAN.

13:26.572 --> 13:31.277
AND HE'S
MADE A MISTAKE.

13:31.277 --> 13:33.613
BUT WE CAN REVERSE
THIS MISTAKE.

13:33.613 --> 13:35.181
THERE'S STILL TIME.

13:35.181 --> 13:38.451
WE CAN TURN IT AROUND
IF WE WORK TOGETH--

13:38.451 --> 13:40.320
[ GASPS ]
PAM!

13:40.320 --> 13:42.255
[ GROANS ]

13:42.255 --> 13:43.456
[ ALL GASP ]

13:44.691 --> 13:47.193
SIR, MAYBE --

13:47.193 --> 13:49.329
YOU SHOULD SHUT
YOUR MOUTH, TOO.

13:50.463 --> 13:53.333
NOW...

13:53.333 --> 13:55.635
PUT ON YOUR SUITS.

13:55.635 --> 13:58.037
OR WE'LL PUT THEM ON
FOR YOU.

14:01.107 --> 14:04.077
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING, GUNFIRE ]

14:04.077 --> 14:06.579
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

14:06.579 --> 14:10.049
[ METAL CLANGS ]

14:10.049 --> 14:13.553
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

14:20.293 --> 14:21.661
Sean: CHARLIE!

14:21.661 --> 14:23.029
HEY, KEYS.
WHERE ARE THE KEYS? THE KEYS?

14:23.029 --> 14:24.097
IN THE GUN LOCKER
OVER THERE!

14:24.097 --> 14:27.400
HURRY! MIKE!
[ KEYS JINGLE ]

14:30.536 --> 14:32.572
COME ON.

14:32.572 --> 14:34.974
[ SIGHS ]

14:34.974 --> 14:36.142
YOU ALL RIGHT?

14:36.142 --> 14:37.377
YEAH.
YEAH?

14:37.377 --> 14:40.079
DID EVERYONE MAKE IT
TO THE ARK?

14:40.079 --> 14:41.347
MOST.

14:41.347 --> 14:43.516
ABBIES ARE EVERYWHERE
OUT THERE NOW.

14:43.516 --> 14:45.184
WE SHOULD STAY HERE.

14:45.184 --> 14:47.253
NO, WE CAN'T.
WE CAN'T.

14:47.253 --> 14:50.256
REMEMBER,
PILCHER ENTRUSTED US

14:50.256 --> 14:53.459
WITH THE FUTURE
OF WAYWARD PINES.

14:53.459 --> 14:56.429
WE HAVE TO MAKE IT
TO THE ARK.

14:56.429 --> 15:00.967
EVERYTHING DEPENDS ON IT --
EVERYTHING.

15:00.967 --> 15:02.068
[ ABBIES SCREAMING ]

15:05.972 --> 15:07.106
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

15:12.078 --> 15:13.279
[ GUN CLICKS ]

15:13.279 --> 15:15.014
Man:
BEHIND YOU!

15:15.014 --> 15:16.115
TIM! RUN!

15:16.115 --> 15:19.051
MY GUN IS JAMMED.

15:19.051 --> 15:21.354
I'M FINE. GO!

15:24.524 --> 15:27.126
[ ABBY ROARS ]
HEADED YOUR WAY!

15:27.126 --> 15:29.195
[ GASPING ]
[ ABBY GROWLING ]

15:36.202 --> 15:39.238
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

15:39.238 --> 15:41.674
[ ABBY SCREECHING ]

15:58.758 --> 16:01.227
[ GUNFIRE ]

16:10.603 --> 16:14.140
[ WOOD CREAKING ]

16:14.140 --> 16:18.010
[ HEAVY FOOTSTEPS ]

16:19.979 --> 16:21.314
[ ABBY ROARS ]

16:21.314 --> 16:22.348
[ GASPING ]

16:24.584 --> 16:26.185
[ ABBY SCREAMING ]

16:26.185 --> 16:27.286
[ GRUNTING ]

16:31.691 --> 16:35.595
[ PANTING ]

16:37.129 --> 16:38.564
Okay. Okay.

16:38.564 --> 16:40.299
Okay. Okay.

16:40.299 --> 16:42.502
Hang on a second.

16:45.538 --> 16:47.573
Okay.

16:47.573 --> 16:50.510
[ GASPS ]

16:50.510 --> 16:53.079
Oh, my God.

16:57.984 --> 17:02.488
[ ALL BREATHING HEAVILY ]

17:02.488 --> 17:04.290
Shh.
IT'S OKAY.

17:04.290 --> 17:07.293
Shh. Shh.

17:18.404 --> 17:20.406
[ AMY BREATHING SHAKILY ]

17:26.212 --> 17:27.980
[ SCREAMS, WHIMPERS ]

17:27.980 --> 17:28.981
STAY THERE.

17:32.552 --> 17:34.487
[ ABBY ROARS ]
MOM!

17:35.521 --> 17:37.256
[ ABBY SCREAMS ]

17:39.225 --> 17:41.260
AH!
[ AMY WHIMPERS ]

17:41.260 --> 17:43.129
IS EVERYONE OKAY?
YEAH.

17:43.129 --> 17:44.597
LET'S GO.
COME ON.

17:44.597 --> 17:46.399
Ethan: HURRY UP. COME ON.
[ GASPING ]

17:46.399 --> 17:48.100
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

17:48.100 --> 17:49.602
[ ABBY GROANING ]

17:52.238 --> 17:54.106
[ ABBY SNARLING ]

17:54.106 --> 17:55.575
[ GASPS ]

17:55.575 --> 17:56.609
TIM.

17:56.609 --> 17:59.612
[ ABBY GROWLING ]

18:20.066 --> 18:25.605
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

18:25.605 --> 18:27.607
WHEW!

18:29.342 --> 18:32.345
[ BRAKES SQUEAK ]

18:40.720 --> 18:43.356
Ethan:
BE CAREFUL GOING DOWN.

18:43.356 --> 18:45.358
ALL RIGHT. I GOT YOU.

18:45.358 --> 18:47.627
[ SIGHS ]
READY. OKAY.

18:50.363 --> 18:52.465
THERE YOU ARE.
COME ON.

18:52.465 --> 18:55.434
THEY'RE COMING.
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

19:12.418 --> 19:15.421
[ SIGHS ]

19:21.027 --> 19:22.528
OKAY.

19:28.601 --> 19:31.237
THOSE TUNNELS --
WHERE DO THEY LEAD TO?

19:31.237 --> 19:32.505
[ SIGHS ]

19:32.505 --> 19:34.607
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

19:34.607 --> 19:36.142
DON'T PLAY DUMB
WITH ME.

19:36.142 --> 19:38.678
YOU'VE BEEN WITH HIM
SINCE THE BEGINNING.

19:38.678 --> 19:39.979
WHERE DO THEY GO?

19:39.979 --> 19:41.247
I DON'T KNOW.

19:41.247 --> 19:43.749
DO YOU WANT EVERYONE IN HERE
TO DIE?

19:43.749 --> 19:46.385
BECAUSE THAT'S
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN.

19:46.385 --> 19:49.655
THE BEST THING WE CAN DO
RIGHT NOW IS STAY CALM.

19:49.655 --> 19:51.257
DAVID <i>WILL</i> RESCUE US.

19:51.257 --> 19:52.491
RESCUE US?!

19:52.491 --> 19:54.527
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?!

19:54.527 --> 19:55.628
HE WANTS US DEAD.

19:55.628 --> 19:57.129
YOU'RE LYING!

19:57.129 --> 19:58.998
Ben:
NO, HE'S NOT.

19:58.998 --> 20:02.334
YOU SAID YOURSELF
THAT PILCHER WATCHES OVER US.

20:02.334 --> 20:04.970
SO IF HE DIDN'T DO THIS,
WHERE IS HE?

20:04.970 --> 20:08.074
HOW COME
WE WEREN'T WARNED?

20:08.074 --> 20:09.241
DAVID DID THIS.

20:09.241 --> 20:11.343
YOU'VE SAID
THIS TOWN IS AN ARK.

20:11.343 --> 20:13.245
ONE CRACK,
AND WE ALL DROWN.

20:13.245 --> 20:15.214
HE IS DROWNING US.

20:16.982 --> 20:18.751
WHERE DO THEY GO?

20:18.751 --> 20:21.320
MEGAN?

20:21.320 --> 20:24.156
WE HAVE NO TIME.

20:29.628 --> 20:31.564
THERE'S A WESTERN TUNNEL.

20:31.564 --> 20:33.265
IT LEADS
TO AN ELEVATOR.

20:33.265 --> 20:34.567
I KNOW THE CODE.

20:34.567 --> 20:39.472
IT WILL TAKE YOU
TO THE MOUNTAIN COMPLEX...

20:39.472 --> 20:40.706
TO DAVID.

20:40.706 --> 20:43.075
GOOD.

20:43.075 --> 20:46.645
THERESA.
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

20:57.223 --> 20:59.391
[ SIGHS ]

21:03.429 --> 21:05.431
Ethan:
ALL RIGHT. THIS IS IT.

21:05.431 --> 21:06.465
HOW ARE WE ON AMMO?

21:06.465 --> 21:09.568
UH,
I'VE GOT TWO MAGS.

21:09.568 --> 21:12.371
I'VE STILL GOT
THESE PIPE BOMBS.

21:12.371 --> 21:14.507
WE GOT TO GET
EVERYBODY MOVING NOW.

21:14.507 --> 21:16.142
WHAT IF PILCHER
SEES US COMING?

21:16.142 --> 21:17.476
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

21:17.476 --> 21:20.980
WE EITHER DEAL WITH HIM
OR WE DEAL WITH THEM.

21:23.282 --> 21:25.050
LET ME GET THE OTHERS.

21:25.050 --> 21:27.353
ALL RIGHT. HERE.

21:27.353 --> 21:29.588
COME BACK HERE.

21:29.588 --> 21:31.690
[ DOOR OPENS ]

21:31.690 --> 21:33.225
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
OW.

21:33.225 --> 21:34.493
ALL RIGHT,
THAT'S IT.

21:34.493 --> 21:35.694
[ SIGHS ]

21:44.436 --> 21:46.505
I'M SORRY
ABOUT HAROLD.

21:49.141 --> 21:51.610
THANK YOU.

21:51.610 --> 21:53.479
YOU REALLY LOVED HIM,
HUH?

21:56.115 --> 21:58.150
YOU KNOW,
PAM SET US UP.

21:58.150 --> 21:59.418
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:59.418 --> 22:02.087
WE COULDN'T HAVE BEEN
MORE DIFFERENT.

22:02.087 --> 22:05.157
SEEMS IMPOSSIBLE TO THINK
THAT WE COULD, UH...

22:07.026 --> 22:09.728
ANYWAY, UM...

22:09.728 --> 22:12.565
SOMETIMES THINGS JUST WORK OUT,
I GUESS.

22:12.565 --> 22:17.269
SOMETIMES PEOPLE
SURPRISE YOU.

22:21.640 --> 22:23.342
THAT'S THE SAFETY.

22:23.342 --> 22:26.712
YOU JUST FLIP IT UP
AND IT'S READY TO GO.

22:26.712 --> 22:27.713
OKAY.

22:30.382 --> 22:32.384
UM...

22:32.384 --> 22:37.523
DAD, I JUST WANTED TO SAY
I'M SORRY ABOUT BEFORE.

22:37.523 --> 22:40.259
AT THE HOSPITAL,
I SAID SOME STUFF...

22:40.259 --> 22:43.062
I HEARD
WHAT YOU SAID.

22:43.062 --> 22:44.697
LOOK.

22:44.697 --> 22:46.999
[ SIGHS ]

22:46.999 --> 22:49.635
YOU'RE MY SON.

22:51.303 --> 22:53.739
I LOVE YOU.

22:53.739 --> 22:56.709
WE'RE GONNA
GET THROUGH THIS.

22:56.709 --> 22:58.377
OKAY?

22:58.377 --> 23:00.346
OKAY.

23:00.346 --> 23:02.348
[ SIGHS ]

23:05.317 --> 23:07.453
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,
LET'S CLEAR OUT.

23:08.754 --> 23:11.156
LET'S GO. COME ON.

23:11.156 --> 23:12.358
Woman: YEAH.

23:12.358 --> 23:14.226
CAREFUL. COME HERE.
COME ON.

23:16.996 --> 23:19.098
MEGAN, COME ON!

23:19.098 --> 23:24.403
I SAW REED AND TRISTAN
AND SARAH OUT ON MAIN STREET.

23:24.403 --> 23:25.537
I'M SURE
THERE ARE OTHERS.

23:28.207 --> 23:30.609
IF THEY'RE NOT HERE,
THEY DIDN'T MAKE IT.

23:30.609 --> 23:32.678
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT.

23:32.678 --> 23:35.147
IF THEY COME,
THEY WON'T BE ABLE TO GET IN

23:35.147 --> 23:36.615
AND THEY'LL DIE
OUT THERE.

23:36.615 --> 23:38.317
SOMEONE HAS TO
STAY BEHIND.

23:38.317 --> 23:39.451
SOMEONE HAS TO
LET THEM IN.

23:39.451 --> 23:41.020
MEGAN, MEGAN, NO.

23:41.020 --> 23:44.156
I MADE A PROMISE
TO THE FIRST GENERATION --

23:44.156 --> 23:48.093
A PROMISE
THAT THEY WOULD BE PROTECTED.

23:48.093 --> 23:50.095
YOU NEED
TO MAKE SURE

23:50.095 --> 23:51.730
THE CHILDREN
GET INTO THE MOUNTAIN COMPLEX.

23:51.730 --> 23:54.266
YOU NEED TO MAKE SURE
THEY'RE SAFE.

23:55.434 --> 23:57.536
I'LL MEET YOU THERE.

23:57.536 --> 23:59.371
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

24:18.123 --> 24:21.126
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

24:31.437 --> 24:34.073
Young woman:
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT. IT'S JASON!

24:34.073 --> 24:35.107
OH. OH, JASON.

24:35.107 --> 24:38.110
[ PANTING ]

24:40.145 --> 24:41.647
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

24:45.718 --> 24:47.720
[ BEEPING ]

24:54.560 --> 24:58.397
Jason: PILCHER PLANNED
FOR A FLOOD LIKE THIS.

24:58.397 --> 25:03.502
HE LEFT THIS --
EVERYTHING WE COULD EVER NEED.

25:08.007 --> 25:11.010
[ ALL MURMURING ]

25:17.249 --> 25:19.385
[ BABY CRIES ]

25:19.385 --> 25:21.086
[ GASPS ]

25:27.393 --> 25:30.129
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

25:30.129 --> 25:33.132
[ ELEVATOR WHIRRING ]

25:37.102 --> 25:40.973
KATE AND I
ARE GONNA GO CHECK IT OUT.

25:40.973 --> 25:43.409
I'LL CALL YOU
ON THIS.

25:46.111 --> 25:48.113
DON'T WORRY.

25:48.113 --> 25:50.249
WE'LL BE FINE.

25:50.249 --> 25:51.483
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO DO THIS
IN GROUPS.

25:51.483 --> 25:53.018
WE'RE GONNA SEND IT
BACK DOWN

25:53.018 --> 25:54.686
AS SOON AS WE KNOW
IT'S SAFE, ALL RIGHT?

25:54.686 --> 25:56.221
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

26:08.734 --> 26:10.702
SLEEP TIGHT.

26:57.296 --> 26:59.076
YOU READY?

26:59.076 --> 27:00.593
READY.

27:05.896 --> 27:10.492
[ GUNFIRE ]

27:10.492 --> 27:12.761
GUARD: Shots fired.
FOLLOW ME!

27:12.761 --> 27:14.596
Shots fired, northeast wing.
MOVE UP!

27:15.597 --> 27:17.800
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

27:19.701 --> 27:21.670
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

27:27.276 --> 27:28.844
WAKE HER UP.

27:28.844 --> 27:32.381
WHAT THE HELL
DO YOU THINK --
I SAID WAKE HER UP.

27:32.381 --> 27:35.317
TAKE THAT SIDE.
OKAY.

27:35.317 --> 27:36.652
ON YOUR RIGHT!
HEY.

27:36.652 --> 27:38.554
FREEZE!
DOWN ON THE GROUND!

27:38.554 --> 27:39.822
DROP YOUR WEAPONS!
DROP IT.

27:39.822 --> 27:41.056
Kate: ON THE FLOOR!
DROP IT!

27:41.924 --> 27:43.592
[ GROANS ]

27:43.592 --> 27:45.894
DAMN IT.
NOW.

27:45.894 --> 27:47.729
DON'T MOVE.

27:47.729 --> 27:50.666
[ HANDCUFFS CLICKING ]

27:54.770 --> 27:56.738
ALL RIGHT, THERESA.
WE'RE GOOD.

27:56.738 --> 27:59.274
Get everybody
in the elevator.

27:59.274 --> 28:01.643
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

28:03.679 --> 28:06.615
[ LOUD CRASH ]

28:06.615 --> 28:08.951
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

28:29.505 --> 28:31.440
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

28:31.440 --> 28:32.541
COME ON. LET'S GO.

28:32.541 --> 28:34.343
GO! GO!
I'LL SEE YOU SOON!

28:34.343 --> 28:35.344
BEN, WAIT!

28:35.344 --> 28:36.879
GO! GO! GO!
WAIT!

28:36.879 --> 28:39.548
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

28:40.916 --> 28:42.918
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

28:42.918 --> 28:44.720
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

28:47.523 --> 28:48.891
STOP!
Man: THAT'S IT! THAT'S IT!

28:48.891 --> 28:50.926
WAIT FOR
THE NEXT LOAD.

28:50.926 --> 28:52.394
OKAY.

28:52.394 --> 28:55.864
[ ABBIES GROWLING, PANTING ]

28:55.864 --> 28:57.499
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

28:57.499 --> 28:58.901
GO!
BE CAREFUL NOW.

28:58.901 --> 29:00.502
Kate:
WE GO TO GO.

29:00.502 --> 29:02.304
LET'S GO.
THERE YOU GO.

29:02.304 --> 29:03.639
STRAIGHT AHEAD, GUYS.

29:03.639 --> 29:04.740
WE CAN'T WAIT!

29:04.740 --> 29:06.575
WE CANNOT WAIT!
LET'S GO!

29:06.575 --> 29:09.611
[ ABBIES SNARLING ]

29:09.611 --> 29:11.547
WHERE'S THERESA?
WHERE'S BEN?

29:11.547 --> 29:13.382
OH,
I HAVEN'T SEEN 'EM YET.

29:13.382 --> 29:15.384
ETHAN,
THEY'RE STILL DOWN THERE.

29:15.384 --> 29:17.519
AND THE ABBIES
ARE INSIDE.

29:17.519 --> 29:19.588
GIVE ME THE BAG.
ETHAN...

29:19.588 --> 29:20.756
GIVE ME THE BAG.

29:20.756 --> 29:21.857
ETHAN...WAIT!

29:24.426 --> 29:25.627
JUST BE CAREFUL.

29:25.627 --> 29:26.728
FIND PILCHER.

29:26.728 --> 29:28.697
MAKE HIM
TURN ON THE POWER.

29:29.765 --> 29:32.601
[ ABBIES SNARLING ]

29:36.872 --> 29:39.575
[ GUN CLICKS ]
BEN!

29:39.575 --> 29:40.809
LET'S GO!

29:40.809 --> 29:41.944
[ ABBIES SCREAMING ]

29:44.813 --> 29:46.415
[ ABBIES GROWLING, SNARLING ]

29:49.418 --> 29:50.619
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

29:57.759 --> 30:00.462
[ POUNDING ]

30:00.462 --> 30:01.496
OKAY.

30:01.496 --> 30:03.732
HOW HIGH
ARE WE GOING?

30:03.732 --> 30:05.500
Ethan: ALL THE WAY
TO THE TOP OF THE MOUNTAIN.

30:09.972 --> 30:11.306
YOU OKAY, SWEETIE?

30:11.306 --> 30:12.407
[ METAL BANGING ]

30:14.843 --> 30:17.446
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

30:17.446 --> 30:20.716
[ ABBIES SNARLING, GROWLING ]

30:29.291 --> 30:31.460
DAD,
THEY'RE IN THE SHAFT.

30:31.460 --> 30:32.794
WHAT?

30:32.794 --> 30:35.697
DAD,
WE HAVE TO GET OUT.

30:35.697 --> 30:36.965
[ BANGING ]

30:36.965 --> 30:39.668
[ ABBIES SNARLING ]

30:42.904 --> 30:45.907
BEN, BEN, TAKE THIS.
HUH?

30:45.907 --> 30:47.342
[ ABBIES SCREAMING ]

30:58.020 --> 31:01.823
WHAT DO YOU SEE
UP THERE?

31:01.823 --> 31:03.825
THERE'S A LADDER!

31:03.825 --> 31:07.029
I SEE THE DOOR.

31:07.029 --> 31:08.964
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

31:18.707 --> 31:20.642
[ ALL GRUNTING ]

31:24.980 --> 31:26.448
YOU READY?
UH-HUH.

31:26.448 --> 31:27.649
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

31:27.649 --> 31:30.786
YOU OKAY?
YEAH?

31:30.786 --> 31:35.557
WHAT'S TAKING THEM
SO LONG?

31:36.858 --> 31:39.795
[ ALL GRUNTING ]

31:39.795 --> 31:45.000
PROMISE ME YOU TWO
ARE GONNA STAY CLOSE, OKAY?

31:45.000 --> 31:46.468
[ SIGHS ]

31:54.509 --> 31:56.812
OKAY.

31:58.313 --> 31:59.915
LET'S GO.

31:59.915 --> 32:02.918
[ ABBIES SNARLING, GROWLING ]

32:12.894 --> 32:16.431
DAD,
GRAB MY HAND.

32:16.431 --> 32:18.734
COME ON.

32:18.734 --> 32:20.969
GO AHEAD.
I'M RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

32:20.969 --> 32:22.304
NO, DAD.

32:22.304 --> 32:23.538
JUST COME UP,
PLEASE.

32:23.538 --> 32:24.706
BEN, COME ON.

32:24.706 --> 32:26.441
WE GOT TO WORK
AS A TEAM HERE.

32:26.441 --> 32:28.276
WE GOT TO KEEP THOSE THINGS
FROM COMING UP.

32:28.276 --> 32:29.344
DAD...

32:29.344 --> 32:31.913
YOUR MOTHER,
AMY, THOSE PEOPLE --

32:31.913 --> 32:34.583
THEY'RE COUNTING ON YOU,
OKAY?

32:34.583 --> 32:35.884
JUST -- JUST GO.

32:35.884 --> 32:37.619
I'M RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

32:39.554 --> 32:41.857
NOW GO! GO!

32:41.857 --> 32:43.525
[ ABBIES ROARING ]

32:46.728 --> 32:49.998
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

33:09.050 --> 33:12.287
[ PEOPLE MURMURING ]

33:12.287 --> 33:15.023
[ BANGING ON DOOR ]

33:19.561 --> 33:21.963
Woman:
OPEN THE DOOR!

33:21.963 --> 33:22.998
LET'S GO.

33:22.998 --> 33:25.267
[ MURMURING CONTINUES ]

33:25.267 --> 33:28.403
[ GRUNTING ]

33:30.872 --> 33:33.308
COME ON.

33:38.280 --> 33:40.015
ALL RIGHT.
COME ON.

34:00.802 --> 34:02.938
David: THEY'RE GOING TO GET UP
THE SHAFT, ETHAN.

34:02.938 --> 34:06.041
AND THEY'RE GONNA
KILL EVERYONE.

34:06.041 --> 34:08.643
I WARNED YOU
THAT REVEALING THE TRUTH

34:08.643 --> 34:10.979
WOULD BE THE DEATH
OF WAYWARD PINES.

34:10.979 --> 34:12.848
BUT YOU WOULDN'T LISTEN.

34:14.649 --> 34:15.851
[ PANTING ]

34:15.851 --> 34:18.386
THE POWER
TO THE FENCE.

34:18.386 --> 34:19.888
TURN IT BACK ON.

34:22.057 --> 34:23.792
NO ONE ELSE HAS TO DIE,
DAVID.

34:23.792 --> 34:25.660
YOU CAN STILL
DO THE RIGHT THING.

34:25.660 --> 34:29.397
I'VE DEDICATED MY ENTIRE LIFE
TO THOSE PEOPLE.

34:29.397 --> 34:31.700
WHO ARE YOU
TO COME IN HERE

34:31.700 --> 34:33.768
AND TELL ME WHAT'S RIGHT
OR WRONG?

34:33.768 --> 34:39.007
YOU'RE ONLY HERE BECAUSE
I CHOSE YOU -- BOTH OF YOU.

34:39.007 --> 34:40.642
[ ABBIES SNARLING ]

34:40.642 --> 34:44.446
WHAT NEITHER OF YOU
EVER UNDERSTOOD

34:44.446 --> 34:47.048
IS THAT THIS TOWN IS NOT
ABOUT ANY ONE INDIVIDUAL.

34:47.048 --> 34:49.718
IT'S NOT
ABOUT FREEDOM.

34:49.718 --> 34:52.687
IT'S ABOUT SOMETHING
MUCH GREATER THAN THAT.

34:52.687 --> 34:56.958
IT'S ABOUT
THE PRESERVATION OF MANKIND.

35:01.296 --> 35:03.832
I HAVE
SACRIFICED EVERYTHING

35:03.832 --> 35:06.768
TO SOW THE SEEDS
FOR ITS FUTURE,

35:06.768 --> 35:08.270
TO PROTECT IT.

35:08.270 --> 35:10.338
ENLIGHTENMENT IS COMING.

35:10.338 --> 35:15.010
MY IDEAS WILL LIVE ON
LONG AFTER I'M GONE.

35:15.010 --> 35:18.313
NO.
YOUR IDEAS END HERE.

35:18.313 --> 35:20.482
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

35:20.482 --> 35:22.617
GO AHEAD.

35:22.617 --> 35:24.619
KILL ME.

35:24.619 --> 35:27.622
YOU CAN'T KILL MY IDEAS.

35:27.622 --> 35:28.757
THEY'RE EVERYWH--

35:28.757 --> 35:29.824
[ GUNSHOT, SHELL CASING CLINKS ]

35:40.535 --> 35:42.437
[ GASPS ]

35:42.437 --> 35:44.739
I'LL TRY
AND GET THE POWER BACK ON.

35:59.421 --> 36:01.056
AMY.

36:01.056 --> 36:03.992
BEN.

36:09.431 --> 36:11.766
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

36:11.766 --> 36:14.769
[ ABBIES GROWLING ]

36:39.060 --> 36:42.564
[ BOMBS WHIRRING ]

36:42.564 --> 36:44.933
[ ABBIES SCREAMING ]

36:55.577 --> 36:57.746
DAD?

36:59.381 --> 37:02.650
[ CRYING ]

37:02.650 --> 37:04.652
DAD?

37:08.656 --> 37:10.658
DAD!

37:27.609 --> 37:29.978
HOW'S BEN?

37:31.513 --> 37:35.450
Kate:
HE'S...STILL UNCONSCIOUS.

37:35.450 --> 37:38.620
I'M LOOKING
FOR BEDS.

37:38.620 --> 37:40.722
PEOPLE ARE TIRED.
THEY NEED TO SLEEP.

37:40.722 --> 37:44.993
OH, THERE ARE BEDS
IN THE EAST WING.

37:44.993 --> 37:47.662
AND HOW ABOUT FOOD,
WATER?

37:47.662 --> 37:51.433
OF COURSE.
I'LL GET THAT ORGANIZED.

37:51.433 --> 37:52.934
PAM?
YEAH.

37:52.934 --> 37:55.837
I WANT TO HELP.

37:55.837 --> 37:59.741
AND, UH, AT THE RISK
OF SOUNDING REDUNDANT,

37:59.741 --> 38:02.844
I'M BETTER
WITH MORE INFORMATION.

38:11.519 --> 38:13.655
Nurse Pam:
QUITE A SIGHT, ISN'T IT?

38:13.655 --> 38:18.493
WHAT IS ALL THIS?

38:18.493 --> 38:22.964
THE REST OF THE POPULATION,
THE ONES WHO HAVEN'T WOKEN YET.

38:22.964 --> 38:24.032
[ BEEPING ]

38:24.032 --> 38:27.469
CAREFUL.

38:27.469 --> 38:29.537
I MIGHT
TAKE YOU SERIOUSLY.

38:29.537 --> 38:30.939
I MEAN IT,
KATE.

38:30.939 --> 38:33.408
I'M TELLING YOU
THE TRUTH.

38:33.408 --> 38:38.480
YOU AND I HAVE NEVER SAID
ONE TRUE THING TO EACH OTHER.

38:38.480 --> 38:41.483
WELL,
LET'S START NOW, THEN, HUH?

38:48.923 --> 38:51.059
Nurse Pam:
IF WE ARE GOING TO SURVIVE,

38:51.059 --> 38:53.328
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO
MAKE IT BETTER.

38:53.328 --> 38:54.662
NO MORE LIES.

38:54.662 --> 38:56.865
NO MORE SURVEILLANCE.

38:56.865 --> 38:58.900
NO MORE RECKONINGS.

38:58.900 --> 39:01.870
IF WE WORK TOGETHER,

39:01.870 --> 39:05.507
I BELIEVE
IT IS POSSIBLE.

39:05.507 --> 39:09.477
I BELIEVE
WE <i>CAN</i> SUCCEED.

39:09.477 --> 39:11.379
WE HAVE TO.

39:11.379 --> 39:13.281
THIS IS IT.

39:13.281 --> 39:16.985
THIS IS
ALL THAT'S LEFT.

39:16.985 --> 39:19.988
THIS IS
THE LAST OF HUMANITY.

39:53.655 --> 39:55.957
Woman:
MR. BURKE?

39:55.957 --> 39:57.492
MR. BURKE?

39:57.492 --> 39:59.694
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

40:04.299 --> 40:06.801
WHERE AM I?

40:06.801 --> 40:10.605
WAYWARD PINES,
OF COURSE.

40:14.042 --> 40:17.478
WHERE IS EVERYONE?

40:17.478 --> 40:19.581
WHY ARE YOU
DRESSED LIKE THAT?

40:19.581 --> 40:23.918
UH,
I'M A NURSE HERE NOW.

40:23.918 --> 40:26.688
UH,
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

40:26.688 --> 40:29.724
I GRADUATED
TWO MONTHS AGO.

40:29.724 --> 40:32.927
I AM MORE THAN QUALIFIED,
MR. BURKE.

40:32.927 --> 40:36.731
WHY ARE YOU
CALLING ME THAT?

40:36.731 --> 40:38.299
GRADUATED?

40:40.969 --> 40:43.571
HOW LONG
WAS I UNCONSCIOUS?

40:43.571 --> 40:45.640
DR. WOODARD WILL BE IN
TO SEE YOU SHORTLY.

40:45.640 --> 40:47.842
YOU CAN ASK HIM ANY QUESTIONS
YOU LIKE, OKAY?

40:47.842 --> 40:49.444
I'M JUST GONNA TAKE
YOUR BLOOD PRESSURE.

40:49.444 --> 40:51.679
AMY...

40:51.679 --> 40:54.582
HOW LONG?

40:54.582 --> 40:57.385
Three years,
four months.

40:57.385 --> 40:58.386
What?

40:58.386 --> 40:59.420
THREE YEARS?

40:59.420 --> 41:00.488
BEN, PLEASE.

41:00.488 --> 41:02.423
PLEASE BE QUIET,
OKAY?

41:04.492 --> 41:06.694
THEY'RE LISTENING.

41:10.665 --> 41:12.800
AFTER YOUR ACCIDENT,

41:12.800 --> 41:15.737
THEY PUT YOU
BACK INTO SUSPENSION

41:15.737 --> 41:18.373
WITH THE REST
OF THE ADULTS.

41:18.373 --> 41:20.375
I TRIED TO GET THEM
TO TAKE YOU OUT EARLIER,

41:20.375 --> 41:24.045
BUT THEY
WOULDN'T ALLOW IT.

41:24.045 --> 41:26.781
THEY'RE ANGRY
AT YOUR FATHER.

41:26.781 --> 41:28.283
WHAT?

41:28.283 --> 41:30.885
THEY BLAME HIM
FOR THE SAVIOR'S DEATH.

41:30.885 --> 41:34.656
THEY THINK
YOU'RE LIKE HIM.

41:34.656 --> 41:39.827
BUT I TOLD THEM,
I CONVINCED THEM...

41:39.827 --> 41:42.797
YOU'RE NOT LIKE HIM.

41:42.797 --> 41:45.433
YOU'RE DIFFERENT.

41:45.433 --> 41:47.502
WHERE ARE MY CLOTHES?
BEN, BEN, WAIT, PLEASE.

41:47.502 --> 41:48.503
WHERE ARE MY CLOTHES?

41:48.503 --> 41:50.271
BEN,
THEY'RE WATCHING.

41:50.271 --> 41:52.307
AND THEY WILL PUT YOU BACK
INTO SUSPENSION WITH THE ADULTS.

41:52.307 --> 41:55.376
AMY,
WHERE ARE MY CLOTHES?

41:57.445 --> 42:01.349
[ CRYING ]

42:02.784 --> 42:05.920
BEN! BEN!

42:08.756 --> 42:11.759
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
BIRDS CHIRPING ]

42:22.337 --> 42:24.405
[ BELL JINGLES ]

42:24.405 --> 42:27.775
[ CHILDREN LAUGHING ]

42:28.976 --> 42:31.479
[ CARNIVAL MUSIC PLAYING ]

43:07.315 --> 43:09.317
[ BICYCLE BELL RINGS ]
